{"tid":319500,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以話我知係咪我錯？","createTime":"2017-07-13T00:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T01:17:21.000Z","uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5067b94c1356a770db15811e3319b3f20060c5","tid":319500,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:19:06.000Z","msg":"尋日既事<br />\n即係我之前同過呢個frd睇過同一隊野既演唱會<br />\n咁今次又有得睇，我要買d內部飛，咪問埋佢<br />\n佢17:22已讀完，又唔覆<br />\n我到17:45先話佢幾句<br />\n(有買過前排內部飛都知要覆得好快，唔係就會比第個要左張飛)<br />\n之後我frd竟然鬧翻我轉頭，仲話係我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到我今朝岩岩起身，佢仲可以繼續鬧緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我其實尋日都問左好多人 (我自己d frd，佢地都話係佢問題,但佢實話我d frd實幫住我)<br />\n<br />\n有人可能會問點解我唔block佢<br />\n我呢個frd好霸道嫁<br />\n話自己無惡意就大晒<br />\n佢話我樣衰，臭閪，以為自己好撚靚，港女，公主病，吊高黎賣etc<br />\n我嬲左/反駁佢，就會比佢話我小器、怒羞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只可以笑下/唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71853ec8532629ddfbdf3263ade843fe4484135","tid":319500,"uid":54490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:37:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cce507a9b02742ae83bfb045fa44e332f16f715","tid":319500,"uid":118700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:40:07.000Z","msg":"下次唔好益佢啦"},{"pid":"b092f1bb61bd0655068d3555dac2c55b077d55fb","tid":319500,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:41:24.000Z","msg":"你肯定佢係你個FD?"},{"pid":"2d05c8cf5f713385f12aa11aa2410aca23da17be","tid":319500,"uid":20074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:53:23.000Z","msg":"笑了<br />\n重同佢做朋友，你都算on 9<br />\n咁都要問人先知邊個對錯，又係on 9"},{"pid":"51580bd0486eddbe767f08b698b74898b722a562","tid":319500,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:16:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你肯定佢係你個FD?</blockquote><br />\n絕過交，和好翻，最近又黎料"},{"pid":"663